Vigen√©re Cipher:

1. Encryption:

	Input:

		Let /home/leela/workspace/VigenereCipher/input file has following text:

			ONCEUPONATIMETHEREWASANOLDWOMANWHOLOVEDBAKINGGINGERBREAD

	Then run the following command:

		java Vigenere -e MYKEYWORD /home/leela/workspace/VigenereCipher/input

	After Encryption the ouput text file is stored at: /home/leela/workspace/VigenereCipher/src/output with the following text:

		ALMISLCEDFGWIRDSIHIYCELKZUZAKKRUDCCRHCNFYGWEJSGXKCNPIHMB


2. Decryption:

	Input:

		Let /home/leela/workspace/VigenereCipher/input file has following text:

			ALMISLCEDFGWIRDSIHIYCELKZUZAKKRUDCCRHCNFYGWEJSGXKCNPIHMB

	Then run the following command:

		java Vigenere -d MYKEYWORD /home/leela/workspace/VigenereCipher/input

	After Decryption the ouput text file is stored at: /home/leela/workspace/VigenereCipher/src/output with the following text:
		
		ONCEUPONATIMETHEREWASANOLDWOMANWHOLOVEDBAKINGGINGERBREAD


